For the most common questions: For the most common questions (after sending the request) مWhat is the next step after sending the request? When the customer sends the order, the store will be notified. The store will verify the availability of the order data and can approve it or reject it, and the customer will be notified accordingly. If it means the stroe approves my order? When the store approves the customer’s request, this means that the store is ready to carry out the request and agrees to communicate with the customer about the request. لWhat should I contact the store? تواصل العميل بالمتجر ربما يكون لعدد اسباب، منها: \n- اذا كانت بيانات الطلب غير متوفرة، مثل اللون او الكمية \n- اذا كانت وسيلة استلام الطلب عبر موقع استلام، وهنا على العميل التواصل مع المتجر حول تحديد موعد الاستلام ومعرفة موقع الاستلام\n- اذا كانت وسيلة استلام المنتج شحن ولم يقم المتجر بتحديد شركة الشحن او سعر الشحن\n- اذا كانت وسيلة استلام المنتج شحن سيكون التواصل لمعرفة رقم الشحنه How will I contact the store if my order is approved? When the store accepts the customer’s request, the request will appear on the customer’s orders page, the customer can contact the store at that time. You have chosen to pay when ordering the product. When should I pay? Payment will be made after the store approves the request with all its details, and the payment will be through a production application. When I choose to pay on demand, do I have to transfer the amount to the store directly? The payment process will be in a production application, and the amount will not go directly to the store until you confirm that the product has been received with the full order details. You have chosen to pay on delivery. How do I pay? Payment will be made upon receipt to the store owner directly, and my production will continue to be verified.
